===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ˌba.ˈjɔ.lə.dʒɪ/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|biologies|-}}

# The science that studies all [[living]] [[matter]] in all its forms, with respect to the living [[organism]] or groups of organisms.
# The forms of life in a place, their behavior and interaction, and the study thereof.
# The structure, function, and behavior of an organism or type of organism.

